# Battle messages
msgid ""
"{winner} defeated {loser}, dealing {damage} damage. {loser} was fatally "
"wounded and perished."
msgstr ""
"{winner} は {loser} を打ち破り、{damage} のダメージを与えた。{loser} は致命傷を負って命を落とした。"

msgid ""
"{winner} defeated {loser}. {loser} took {loser_dmg} damage, {winner} also "
"took {winner_dmg} damage."
msgstr ""
"{winner} は {loser} を打ち破った。{loser} は {loser_dmg} のダメージを受け、{winner} も {winner_dmg} のダメージを負った。"
